you already quit your job.

357
00:19:16,130 --> 00:19:17,760
I'll move out
and live alone for a while.

358
00:19:18,060 --> 00:19:19,730
Of course, you will!

359
00:19:19,730 --> 00:19:22,670
Were you going to stay here
after causing all this trouble?

360
00:19:22,670 --> 00:19:23,800
What kind of human
could do such a thing?

361
00:19:23,800 --> 00:19:24,970
Honey.

362
00:19:25,300 --> 00:19:28,010
Even if you'd wanted to stay,
I was going to kick you out.

363
00:19:29,910 --> 00:19:31,480
I'll be in my room.

364
00:19:32,480 --> 00:19:33,980
Grandma. Let's go to your room.

365
00:19:34,480 --> 00:19:35,650
Get out this instant!

366
00:19:47,160 --> 00:19:49,890
Ji Hyuk, you can't leave like this
after saying all that.

367
00:19:51,300 --> 00:19:52,530
What am I supposed to say, then?

368
00:19:53,260 --> 00:19:55,170
Is there a correct answer
for this situation?

369
00:19:55,170 --> 00:19:56,930
Like saying, "It's all my fault?"

370
00:19:56,930 --> 00:19:58,970
Of course, you have to say that.

371
00:19:59,140 --> 00:20:00,400
I did apologize.

372
00:20:01,370 --> 00:20:02,870
I do feel bad...

373
00:20:03,710 --> 00:20:04,710
that I brought shame on them.

374
00:20:05,140 --> 00:20:06,340
That's all I can say.

375
00:20:07,280 --> 00:20:08,810
But that's not my fault.

376
00:20:08,810 --> 00:20:11,580
You tried to marry for money
and disgraced our family.

377
00:20:11,580 --> 00:20:13,120
And it's not your fault?

378
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:14,920
I should get changed.
Get out, both of you.

379
00:20:14,920 --> 00:20:15,950
