- Stop it.

438
00:24:25,400 --> 00:24:26,470
We will get going.

439
00:24:26,470 --> 00:24:27,870
- Bye, guys!
- Ji Hyuk must be devastated.

440
00:24:27,870 --> 00:24:29,910
