to kill yourself or what?

488
00:27:33,960 --> 00:27:35,160
You're not a ghost, are you?

489
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,990
You're
the living Lee Sang Cheol, right?

490
00:27:38,330 --> 00:27:39,460
Darn it.

491
00:27:40,260 --> 00:27:41,830
- My gosh.
- What?

492
00:27:46,270 --> 00:27:47,340
Honey.

493
00:27:51,810 --> 00:27:52,880
Da Jeong.

494
00:27:53,510 --> 00:27:54,810
I thought...

