and that it wasn't a big deal.

507
00:28:43,690 --> 00:28:45,600
That darn brat.

508
00:28:46,530 --> 00:28:47,660
What a jerk.

509
00:28:49,430 --> 00:28:50,470
My gosh.

510
00:28:51,430 --> 00:28:52,570
